message.content:
Ecco una landing page single-file in stile cyberpunk per un negozio di programmazione AI, con modulo contatti e popup di conferma.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Code Emporium • Cyberpunk</title>
    <!-- Font futuristico -->
    <link href="https://https" equiv="preconnect" crossorigin>
    <style>
    /* reset base */
    *,
    *,
    *,
    *::before,
    *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    body {
        background: #000000 radial-gradient circle at 10% 10%, #00 0%, #000 100%;
        font-family: 'system-1', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 0;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        background: #0c0c0c;
        background-image: 
        linear-gradient to bottom, #0f0f1e 0%, #0a0a0f 100%;
        background-attachment: fixed;
    }

    /* main grid */
    .page {
        max-width: 1280px;
        width: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        border: 1px solid #0ff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff, 0 0 40px #0ff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        transition: box-shadow 0.3s;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    /* header */
    header {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed ##0ff;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .logo {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff, 0 0 20px #0ff;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient 45deg, #0ff, #f0f, #0ff;
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .logo span {
        background: #0ff;
        color: #000;
        padding: 0 4px;
        border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.2rem;
        list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
        color: #0ff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 300;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
        border-color: #0ff;
        background: #0ff20;
        color: #000;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff;
    }

    /* hero */
    .hero {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        gap: 1.2rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff, 0 0 20px #0ff;
        background: linear-gradient 45deg, #0ff, #f0f, #0ff;
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero p {
        max-width: 600px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #b0b0ff;
        text-shadow: 0 0 2px #0ff;
    }

    .cta-button {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid #0ff;
    color: #0ff;
    padding: 0.8rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.3s;
    border-radius: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px #0ff, inset 0 0 5px #0ff;
    background: #0ff1;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    display: inline-block;
    text-decoration: none;
}

    .cta-button:hover {
    background: #0ff;
    color: #000;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff, 0 0 40px #0ff;
    transform: scale(1.1);
}

    /* features */
    .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr);
    gap: 1.2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
}

    .card {
    background: #0a0a0f;
    border: 1px solid #0ff;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px #0ff, inset 0 0 5px #0ff;
    transition: 0.3s;
    border-radius: 4px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
}

    .card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px #0ff, 0 0 20px #0ff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: #0f0f1e;
}

    .card i {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #0ff;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff;
}

    .card h3 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #f0f;
    text-shadow: 0 0 2px #f0f;
}

    .card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #b0b0ff;
}

    /* form */
    .form-wrapper {
    background: #0a0a0f;
    border: 1px solid #0ff;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px #0ff, inset 0 0 5px #0ff;
    border-radius: 4px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
}

    .form-wrapper h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    color: #0ff;
    text-shadow: 0 0 2px #0ff;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}

    .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
}

    label {
    color: #0ff;
    font-weight: lighter;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

    input, textarea, select {
    background: #000;
    border: 1px solid #0ff;
    padding: 0.8rem 0.5rem;
    color: #0ff;
    font-size: 1rem;
    outline: none;
    transition: 0.2s;
    border-radius: 2px;
    width: 100%;
    font-family: inherit;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 5px #0ff;
}

    input:focus, textarea:focus {
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff, inset 0 0 10px #0ff;
        border-color: #f0f;
    background: #0f0f0f;
}

    textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 80px;
}

    .form-button {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid #0ff;
    color: #0ff;
    padding: 0.8rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.3s;
    border-radius: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px #0ff, inset 0 0 5px #0ff;
    background: #0ff1;
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 1rem;
}

    .form-button:hover {
    background: #0ff;
    color: #000;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff, 0 0 40px #0ff;
    transform: scale(1.1);
}

    /* footer */
    footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-top: 1px dashed #0ff;
    color: #0ff;
    font-size: 0.1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
}

    footer a {
    color: #f0f;
    text-decoration: none;
}

    footer a:hover {
    text-shadow: 0 0 2px #f0f;
}

    /* popup overlay */
    .popup-overlay {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
        z-index: 999;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        transition: opacity 0.0.0.3s;
    }

    .popup-overlay attivi {
        display: flex;
    }

    .popup-box {
        background: #0a0a0f;
        border: 2px solid #0ff;
        padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff, 0 0 40px #0ff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        max-width: 300px;
        width: 90%;
        animation: fadeIn 0.3s;
    }

    .popup-box h2 {
        color: #0ff;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .popup-box p {
        color: #b0b0ff;
    }

    .popup-box .close-btn {
        background: transparent;
        border: 1px solid #0ff;
        color: #0ff;
        padding: 0.5rem 2.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.2rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.2s;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .popup-box .close-btn:hover {
        background: #0ff;
        color: #000;
    }

    /* responsive */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    .nav-links {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .page {
        padding: 1rem;
    }
    .form-wrapper {
        padding: 1rem;
    }
    }
</style>
    <!-- JS script -->
    <script>
        /* popup */
        .popup-overlay {
            display: none;
        }
        .popup-overlay.show {
            display: flex;
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <!-- header -->
        <header>
            <div class="logo">AI <span>Code</span> Emporium</div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Servizi</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">AI</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contatti</a></li>
            </ul>
        </header>

        <!-- hero -->
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>AI Code Emporium</h1>
            <p>Il tuo codice è oltre il limite. Programmazione AI, potenza quantistica, sistemi neurali prigionieri.</p>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">ACCendi Ora</a>
        </section>

        <!-- features -->
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <i>�</i>
                <h3>Neal Link</h3>
                <p>Accesso diretto alla matrice, velocità di calcolo quantistica.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i>⚡</i>
                <h3>Synzed</h3>
                <p>Pena di elaborazione AI, ottimizzazione dei flussi.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i>🧠</i>
                <h3>Deep Core</h3>
                <p>Appenzamento neurale, memoria espessa.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <i>🕸️</i>
                <h3>Matrix</h3>
                <p>Rete di calcolo distribuita, nodi di AI.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- modulo contatti -->
        <div class="form-wrapper">
            <h2>ContAtto • AI</h2>
            <form id="contactForm">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="nome">Nome</label>
                    <input type="text" id="nome" name="nome" placeholder="Il tuo nome" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="tuo@dominio.com" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="richiesta">Richiesta</label>
                    <textarea id="richiesta" name="richiesta" placeholder="Scaccia la tua richiesta..."></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="priorità">Priorità</label>
                    <select id="priorità" name="priorità">
                        <option value="urg">Urg</option>
                        <option value="norm">Norm</option>
                        <option value="alta">Alta</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="form-button" id="submitBtn">TrasVia • Messaggio</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- footer -->
        <footer>
            <p>© 202 Anno • AI Code Emporium — <a href="#">Nella Matrice</a></p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <!-- popup overlay -->
    <div class="popup-overlay" id="popupOverlay">
        <div class="popup-box">
            <h2>✅ Richiesta Inviata</h2>
            <p>Il tuo messaggio è stato recato nella rete neurale. Risposta imminente.</p>
            <button class="close-btn" id="closePopup">OK • Chiudi</button>
        </div>
    </div>

